About:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
JavaScript Window Manager (and simple desktop environment) for modern browsers.
Uses PHP+MySQL backend and Glade for frontend. AJAX is used to perform events
and access the Application API.

Building applications:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Follow the example. After modifications you have to run './bin/application-gen'

Notes for author:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Touch devices:
* http://forum.jquery.com/topic/jquery-ui-and-touch-devices
  * http://code.google.com/p/jquery-ui-for-ipad-and-iphone/
  * https://github.com/furf/jquery-ui-touch-punch

